act/164879/', '', 'Upadacitinib, Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Thalidomide, More', 1767369485);
